                                            Cheap is expensive, don't you know?
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>We all need charging cables, and the costs can add up quickly. So it's tempting to simply order the cheapest cables you can find and call it a day. However, saving a few dollars on charging cables can end up costing you much more than it saves you in the short term.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Mon, 08 Sep 2025 21:31:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/hidden-dangers-of-cheap-charging-cables/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[If I Only Had $400 for a Work PC, Here’s What I’d Do]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/if-i-only-had-400-for-a-work-pc-heres-what-id-do/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Ismar Hrnjicevic]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/52844692712_16be54b0a6_o.jpg" length="269" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Windows]]></category><category><![CDATA[laptops]]></category><category><![CDATA[pc building]]></category><category><![CDATA[Ajazz AK820]]></category><description><![CDATA[
